1
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:09,520
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

2
00:00:10,920 --> 00:00:13,440
<i>until the day I understand.</i>

3
00:00:14,360 --> 00:00:15,999
<i>When it comes to resilience,</i>

4
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:21,520
<i>I am someone forged from losses
I was never ready for.</i>

5
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:24,200
<i>And I've come to believe</i>

6
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:28,599
<i>that loving someone is simply</i>

7
00:00:28,600 --> 00:00:31,880
<i>another name for the courage to lose.</i>

8
00:00:36,120 --> 00:00:39,160
<i>I'm glad she's finally asleep.</i>

9
00:00:40,080 --> 00:00:44,440
{\an8}She wouldn't let go
of this toy tank until she fell asleep.

10
00:00:45,120 --> 00:00:47,040
{\an8}I feel sorry for her, but...

11
00:00:47,760 --> 00:00:48,960
{\an8}But thank God.

12
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:53,320
{\an8}Thank God. You did a great job.

13
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:58,120
{\an8}When the time comes,
it will be our daughter.

14
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,040
{\an8}Sure?

15
00:01:00,640 --> 00:01:02,159
{\an8}Pray for us

16
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:04,759
{\an8}that we'll have a daughter as cute as her.

17
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:05,960
{\an8}Of course.

18
00:01:08,080 --> 00:01:09,000
{\an8}Well...

19
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:10,760
{\an8}But...

20
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:15,520
{\an8}I miss Radwa.

21
00:01:16,520 --> 00:01:18,200
{\an8}So much.

22
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:26,160
We all miss her.

23
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:30,120
But your brother

24
00:01:30,880 --> 00:01:33,000
misses his wife even more.

25
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,360
We have to be strong

26
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:40,400
for Ridz.

27
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:46,720
Peace be upon you.

28
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:50,000
- Peace be upon you too, Ridz.
- Peace be upon you too, Ridz.

29
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:52,839
I took this toy tank

30
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:57,039
because Tia wouldn't let it go
until she fell asleep.

31
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:59,039
She was crying. I felt sorry for her.

32
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:01,559
No, Ridz. I was the one who took it out.

33
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:03,799
- Sorry.
- Sorry, Ridz.

34
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,560
Thank you for looking after Tia.

35
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:09,560
You guys can go back now.

36
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:17,560
I've ironed your clothes for tomorrow.
They're in the closet.

37
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,599
Come on.

38
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:22,320
Ridz, I'm sorry.

39
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:06,840
Darling, I can't lose you.

40
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:13,000
I love you so much.

41
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:18,800
And I love you too, Thariq Ridzuwan.

42
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:52,760
I miss you so much.

43
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:23,080
Happy tenth anniversary, darling.

44
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,560
For our family.

45
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,840
Tia was playing with your toy tank.

46
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,640
She loves it. Right?

47
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:42,640
She's just as weird as her mom.

48
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:50,120
Darling.

49
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:54,040
I'll officially be replacing Dad

50
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,080
as the hotel's CEO today.

51
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,880
You're fine with me quitting, right?

52
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:09,720
There will be no mission

53
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,720
and no risky job.

54
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:18,000
So I can focus on Tia

55
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:23,280
more than I did on you.

56
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:31,760
I miss you so much, my treasure.

57
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,960
And our precious Tia misses you too.

58
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:48,880
Even though she will never get
to see her mom,

59
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,360
I will make sure

60
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:57,560
that she knows who her mom is.

61
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:04,520
And that she will love her mom.

62
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:12,840
Every moment of the day.

63
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:22,520
Want to chat with me?

64
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,960
Do you?

65
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:30,000
Listen.

66
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:34,080
You must remember our words.

67
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,960
Live well.

68
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:42,280
Be a humble person.

69
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,360
Have patience.

70
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:50,240
Hold back your anger and disappointment.

71
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:55,920
Accept every fate that God has determined.

72
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,920
May God

73
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:06,000
ease everything for Tia Radia
binti Thariq Ridzuwan.

74
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:18,240
I won't forget what you said to me.

75
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:25,040
<i>Thariq Ridzuwan,</i>

76
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:31,160
<i>your shoulder is
my favorite place to rest.</i>

77
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:36,320
<i>Your warm embrace feels just like home.</i>

78
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:43,200
<i>Even a single smile from you
can heal a thousand of my wounds.</i>

79
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:50,520
<i>I'm sorry if I've ever fallen short
of being the good wife you deserve.</i>

80
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:57,240
<i>I'm giving you the gift
of a child, my love.</i>

81
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,959
<i>Hold her close and love her</i>

82
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:04,560
<i>just as deeply as you have loved me.</i>

83
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:23,360
I promise

84
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:27,280
I'll take care of our precious Tia

85
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:33,360
a thousand times better
than I took care of you.

86
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:40,039
No one can ever harm her.

87
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:42,720
I promise.

88
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,920
Peace be upon you, darling.

89
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:56,520
Let's go. Come with me.

90
00:08:57,760 --> 00:09:01,440
Say goodbye to your mom. Bye, Mama.

91
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:20,519
Yes, baby. I'm here.

92
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:22,160
I'm here.

93
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,320
Hold on.

94
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:29,600
Usually, the Megah Holding CEO
would come walking

95
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:32,120
with at least five bodyguards.

96
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:35,560
But our Thariq Ridzuwan
came with a stroller.

97
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:40,559
Gosh. While carrying a bag of diapers.

98
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:41,760
That's rare.

99
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:46,199
Yes, baby.

100
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,520
Hi.

101
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:52,000
See? She's happy to see me.

102
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,400
Everybody's happy.

103
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:57,639
Of course she is.

104
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:59,879
Kids love monkeys. Right?

105
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:02,999
Don't say that. It's not nice.

106
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:05,039
Look at your ears. Just like monkeys.

107
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:09,680
Peace be upon you. In the name of God.

108
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:14,800
- My gosh.
- What a cute little girl.

109
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:20,679
Why do you want to hold her so much?
You have your own child.

110
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:23,040
So what? I miss my baby.

111
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,320
Right?

112
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:30,400
Ridz, sorry.

113
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:35,320
- Ridz, about the toy tank, I--
- Thalia.

114
00:10:37,160 --> 00:10:38,080
Thank you.

115
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:42,640
Thank you for ironing our clothes.

116
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:47,280
Guys, thank you
for always being there for me.

117
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:51,680
Are you ready?

118
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:55,879
Dad couldn't wait to make you the new CEO.

119
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:57,920
His speech is really short.

120
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,039
Ready.

121
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:07,240
- Baby Tia!
- No.

122
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:11,439
I just want to hold her. Don't get mad.

123
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:13,439
What do you mean?

124
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:16,200
Your face is annoying.
Your voice is too loud.

125
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,240
Can you get lost?

126
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,520
I said

127
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:24,440
get lost.

128
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:32,200
Thank you for supporting
our company all this time.

129
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:37,160
I hope you will give the same support

130
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:41,680
to my new replacement.

131
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:46,920
So, without further ado,

132
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:50,960
let me introduce my replacement.

133
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:53,759
Thariq Ridzuwan.

134
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:55,040
Yeah!

135
00:11:58,680 --> 00:12:00,760
New CEO. Let's go, Ridz!

136
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,080
Let's go!

137
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:15,279
Ridz!

138
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,680
Let's go, Ridz!

139
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,319
Did I miss anything?

140
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:24,040
What are you doing here?

141
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,920
Let me hold her.

142
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:43,999
Tia? Aina! Tia!

143
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,879
- Where's Tia?
- Ridz!

144
00:12:45,880 --> 00:12:47,840
Aina took Tia away, Ridz!

145
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:54,319
Two of you. Kevin, check the CCTV.

146
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:55,760
Upstairs.

147
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:51,559
Megat, check the back seat.

148
00:13:51,560 --> 00:13:52,840
Haider, check the trunk.

149
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:01,639
- Clear.
- Bitch.

150
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:03,039
Nothing?

151
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:06,280
Where's Tia?

152
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:13,080
Where's my daughter?

153
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:16,080
I gave her to him.

154
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:18,680
Who is he?

155
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:21,879
He said if I help him,

156
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:24,120
he won't bother us and we can get married.

157
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:25,720
Who?

158
00:14:26,920 --> 00:14:28,959
He asked me to kidnap Tia.

159
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:31,720
- Who is it?
- Radwa!

160
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,800
Guys, I found it.

161
00:15:02,640 --> 00:15:05,000
Farez!

162
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:12,559
Kevin, check the CCTV footage
and traffic cams.

163
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:13,960
Track Farez's car.

164
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:15,800
Got it.

165
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:20,800
I will get Mr. Nasir's approval.

166
00:15:22,160 --> 00:15:25,119
Haider, go to the camp.

167
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:27,040
Standby gears and weapons.

168
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:29,960
Daniel and Megat,

169
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:32,720
get our informers in KL.

170
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,080
Get some info.

171
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:39,480
KL isn't that big.
Someone must have seen him.

172
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:45,160
Ridz, follow me.

173
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:48,160
Ridz.

174
00:15:51,040 --> 00:15:52,160
Today

175
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:57,840
is my anniversary with Tia

176
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,040
and Radwa.

177
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:09,640
Today

178
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:17,760
is the day that I finally accepted
that Radwa is gone.

179
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:20,760
Today...

180
00:16:24,400 --> 00:16:26,080
For almost a year,

181
00:16:29,920 --> 00:16:31,920
I tried to smile again.

182
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:38,680
I finally feel strong enough
to live again.

183
00:16:42,120 --> 00:16:43,760
But Farez came

184
00:16:47,400 --> 00:16:49,560
and took Tia away from me.

185
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:55,360
I promised Radwa

186
00:17:00,400 --> 00:17:06,119
that I'll take care of Tia a thousand
times better than I ever took care of her.

187
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:13,520
No one can touch her.

188
00:17:15,640 --> 00:17:17,520
That was my promise.

189
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:23,440
Now, I'm trying to understand.

190
00:17:27,280 --> 00:17:29,400
What have I done wrong?

191
00:17:33,080 --> 00:17:36,000
What is going on in my life?

192
00:17:38,360 --> 00:17:43,000
What have I done
that God is testing me this much?

193
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:54,160
Be honest with me, Ridz.

194
00:17:57,960 --> 00:18:00,280
You're the one who was on the prayer mat.

195
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,920
You're the one who prostrated.

196
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:07,640
You're the one who prayed.

197
00:18:09,760 --> 00:18:12,680
You were the one crying,
pouring your heart out to God just now.

198
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:16,760
So tell me.

199
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:20,400
Do you think this is a punishment

200
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:24,200
or a test from God?

201
00:18:26,440 --> 00:18:28,200
My eyes

202
00:18:31,760 --> 00:18:33,000
and my brain

203
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:37,880
believe that this is a punishment.

204
00:18:42,280 --> 00:18:43,720
But my heart

205
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:50,600
believes that this is a test.

206
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:55,400
Eyes can see it wrong.

207
00:18:58,680 --> 00:18:59,680
Our brains

208
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:05,880
aren't smart enough
to understand God's greatness.

209
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:10,120
But the heart...

210
00:19:11,240 --> 00:19:13,640
of someone kind like you

211
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:18,080
will never lie.

212
00:19:20,280 --> 00:19:23,200
So, you have to keep believing

213
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:26,360
that this is all just a test.

214
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:31,280
Keep trusting in God.

215
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:36,360
With every hardship

216
00:19:37,840 --> 00:19:39,800
comes ease.

217
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:46,720
I was proud before God.

218
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:53,360
I doubted Him.

219
00:20:00,120 --> 00:20:02,320
I will never repeat the same mistake.

220
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:08,400
This is my test.

221
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:13,720
Truly,

222
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:17,360
with every hardship

223
00:20:20,040 --> 00:20:21,920
comes ease.

224
00:20:32,040 --> 00:20:34,400
We'll save Tia today.

225
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:39,680
We'll save my daughter.

226
00:21:09,040 --> 00:21:11,279
<i>There is no deity except You.</i>

227
00:21:11,280 --> 00:21:12,919
<i>Exalted are You.</i>

228
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:15,120
<i>Indeed, I am among the wrongdoers.</i>

229
00:21:16,640 --> 00:21:18,719
<i>There is no deity but Allah.</i>

230
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:20,800
<i>Muhammad is His messenger.</i>

231
00:21:33,840 --> 00:21:35,080
Where is he?

232
00:21:38,760 --> 00:21:39,680
Contact.

233
00:21:58,480 --> 00:21:59,560
Megat,

234
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:03,120
call Adrean now.

235
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:24,440
<i>- Hello, sir. On the move.</i>
- Okay.

236
00:22:34,720 --> 00:22:37,360
Lead the way, Demonio.

237
00:22:38,840 --> 00:22:43,279
I think they're heading to the airport.
We're heading that way.

238
00:22:43,280 --> 00:22:44,959
He can't be taking a commercial flight.

239
00:22:44,960 --> 00:22:46,640
He might be taking Tia out of the country.

240
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:50,679
There's an area in KLIA2. Head there.

241
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:52,199
Check over there.

242
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:55,359
There's a flight scheduled
to fly off from the hangar tonight.

243
00:22:55,360 --> 00:22:56,359
Really?

244
00:22:56,360 --> 00:23:00,040
Kevin, Haider, have you blocked
the road they'll be taking?

245
00:23:01,080 --> 00:23:02,439
Yes, it's blocked.

246
00:23:02,440 --> 00:23:04,080
Adrean, stop.

247
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:06,840
Why are we stopping here?

248
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:10,719
I know Farez. He must have a backup plan.
You can go first.

249
00:23:10,720 --> 00:23:12,200
- I'll catch up.
- Ridz.

250
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:13,879
Are you sure?

251
00:23:13,880 --> 00:23:16,199
Just go. I promise I'll come.

252
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:17,599
All right?

253
00:23:17,600 --> 00:23:19,639
Be careful, Ridz.

254
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:21,400
If God wills it.

255
00:23:31,360 --> 00:23:33,520
CAUTION
ROAD CLOSURE

256
00:23:37,440 --> 00:23:38,679
What's going on?

257
00:23:38,680 --> 00:23:40,239
Roads are closed.

258
00:23:40,240 --> 00:23:41,519
Have a look.

259
00:23:41,520 --> 00:23:43,200
Yes, sir. Come.

260
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:51,760
Why are you blocking the road?
Let us pass.

261
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:54,360
Will you let us pass or die?

262
00:24:01,400 --> 00:24:02,839
Hey.

263
00:24:02,840 --> 00:24:05,199
Don't start shooting here.

264
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:06,959
My daughter wants to sleep.

265
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:09,159
That's not your daughter!

266
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:11,080
It's Thariq Ridzuwan's!

267
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:25,760
They're playing us!

268
00:24:47,520 --> 00:24:49,359
Change of plans.

269
00:24:49,360 --> 00:24:51,879
Meet me at the location I just sent you.

270
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:53,720
<i>I'm fleeing overseas.</i>

271
00:25:56,080 --> 00:25:57,320
Treasure?

272
00:26:10,360 --> 00:26:12,320
I came here

273
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:15,200
to kill you,

274
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:17,960
Thariq Ridzuwan.

275
00:26:19,280 --> 00:26:21,560
But when I found out
that you have a daughter,

276
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:29,080
I found the most painful revenge.

277
00:26:30,760 --> 00:26:33,200
Dying is too easy for you.

278
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:38,760
I want you to feel what I feel.

279
00:26:40,760 --> 00:26:47,040
I want you to feel how painful it is
to lose a child after you killed mine.

280
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:56,680
Now, release my husband

281
00:26:57,960 --> 00:27:00,360
if you love your daughter.

282
00:27:02,840 --> 00:27:04,680
But Tia is our child.

283
00:27:21,720 --> 00:27:23,200
How are you, my friend?

284
00:27:24,960 --> 00:27:26,280
Long time no see.

285
00:27:28,520 --> 00:27:30,520
You look like you lost weight.

286
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:33,200
Like someone who just lost his wife.

287
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:39,560
Like someone who craves love.

288
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:01,840
Damn!

289
00:28:52,240 --> 00:28:53,400
Damn it.

290
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:17,520
You tried to kill me back then.

291
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:20,240
You failed.

292
00:30:23,120 --> 00:30:25,200
I never tried to kill you.

293
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:28,760
Farez,

294
00:30:30,560 --> 00:30:32,000
control your emotions.

295
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:35,800
We...

296
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:39,800
We're not angels

297
00:30:41,080 --> 00:30:42,720
who never make mistakes.

298
00:30:45,520 --> 00:30:47,440
We're also not demons

299
00:30:48,400 --> 00:30:50,000
who have no kindness at all.

300
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:54,120
We are humans.

301
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:57,480
We have our own strengths

302
00:30:58,800 --> 00:31:00,320
and weaknesses.

303
00:31:03,120 --> 00:31:03,960
Farez.

304
00:31:05,960 --> 00:31:08,120
Every prayer we make to God

305
00:31:09,600 --> 00:31:11,199
will be answered.

306
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:14,080
Enough. Farez, enough.

307
00:31:16,200 --> 00:31:17,640
Your dad...

308
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:22,239
His existence in your life

309
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:24,480
was your test.

310
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:28,400
This is my test. And I accept it.

311
00:31:29,840 --> 00:31:30,920
You want to shoot me?

312
00:31:32,840 --> 00:31:33,960
Shoot.

313
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:37,920
Just go for it.

314
00:31:38,680 --> 00:31:41,440
But just so you know,

315
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:43,760
Radwa...

316
00:31:45,520 --> 00:31:47,080
will never love you.

317
00:31:48,080 --> 00:31:49,079
Ever.

318
00:31:49,080 --> 00:31:50,480
Shoot.

319
00:31:51,320 --> 00:31:52,600
Shoot me, Farez. Go.

320
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:00,400
My dad was right.

321
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:06,440
I live in this nightmare every day.

322
00:32:08,120 --> 00:32:10,280
This life doesn't suit me.

323
00:32:13,760 --> 00:32:15,120
Thank you, Ridz.

324
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,960
Thank you for listening.

325
00:32:18,760 --> 00:32:19,640
Farez...

326
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:23,400
Goodbye, friend.

327
00:32:26,840 --> 00:32:28,320
Be happy.

328
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:38,400
And if I can't have Radwa,

329
00:32:40,920 --> 00:32:41,840
neither can you.

330
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:28,199
All these women

331
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:30,120
look similar.

332
00:33:31,040 --> 00:33:32,479
But they're not the same.

333
00:33:32,480 --> 00:33:36,279
I want her to have
the same height as Husniya Radwa!

334
00:33:36,280 --> 00:33:38,039
The bone structure,

335
00:33:38,040 --> 00:33:40,640
size, and everything
must be the same! Understood?

336
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:45,959
Can I really be an idol?

337
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:47,719
A great singer?

338
00:33:47,720 --> 00:33:50,440
I will take you to South Korea myself.

339
00:33:51,120 --> 00:33:53,560
I know the owner of one of the agencies.

340
00:33:54,520 --> 00:33:56,080
Korea?

341
00:33:57,640 --> 00:33:59,560
Thank you. I'm so happy.

342
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:02,400
But there's a condition.

343
00:34:03,840 --> 00:34:05,960
We have to fix your face.

344
00:34:07,080 --> 00:34:10,079
Is it okay?
We'll make you look more beautiful.

345
00:34:10,080 --> 00:34:11,920
Add dimples.

346
00:34:12,480 --> 00:34:16,239
We can also polish your voice.

347
00:34:16,840 --> 00:34:21,159
I mean, you have to sacrifice
to be an idol.

348
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:24,360
Thank you!

349
00:34:30,719 --> 00:34:31,800
Are you ready?

350
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:44,400
Perfect.

351
00:34:49,679 --> 00:34:52,000
OMG.

352
00:34:54,080 --> 00:34:56,159
So pretty!

353
00:34:57,560 --> 00:35:02,960
Honey, you haven't told me
why we're back in Malaysia.

354
00:35:03,760 --> 00:35:07,159
I mean, I can't be an idol here.

355
00:35:07,160 --> 00:35:09,480
What about my training?

356
00:35:10,120 --> 00:35:14,120
And then, why do I have to wear this?

357
00:35:14,720 --> 00:35:16,680
It's suffocating, you know?

358
00:35:17,280 --> 00:35:20,480
I've never seen idols wearing this.

359
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:32,000
Your voice disgusts me.

360
00:35:39,360 --> 00:35:40,880
Your face is perfect.

361
00:35:42,080 --> 00:35:43,480
Beautiful.

362
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:46,920
But your voice isn't.

363
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:13,400
Make sure you leave no scars
after stitching.

364
00:36:14,120 --> 00:36:15,560
Don't get caught.

365
00:36:16,440 --> 00:36:17,280
Clean.

366
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:19,319
Also,

367
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:20,400
freeze her.

368
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:23,320
Okay, boss.

369
00:36:24,080 --> 00:36:28,120
For the labor wound, do it properly.

370
00:36:29,160 --> 00:36:32,160
They have to believe
that Lily was Husniya.

371
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:33,839
Understand?

372
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:35,400
Understood, boss.

373
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:41,560
Husniya will deliver anytime.

374
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:43,720
Did you speak with the nurse?

375
00:36:44,640 --> 00:36:45,920
All done.

376
00:38:19,640 --> 00:38:20,640
Hurry up.

377
00:38:42,640 --> 00:38:43,680
I'm sorry.

378
00:38:46,720 --> 00:38:48,399
If she dies,

379
00:38:48,400 --> 00:38:49,799
you die.

380
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:50,759
Please don't.

381
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,160
Do what you have to do.

382
00:38:53,520 --> 00:38:55,240
- Now!
- Nurse.

383
00:39:44,640 --> 00:39:45,920
Good morning, darling.

384
00:39:56,080 --> 00:39:57,240
Where am I?

385
00:39:59,240 --> 00:40:00,440
Our home.

386
00:40:03,120 --> 00:40:04,200
Who are you?

387
00:40:05,160 --> 00:40:07,160
I can't remember anything at all.

388
00:40:08,200 --> 00:40:10,320
I'm Farez, your husband.

389
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:25,280
We look so happy together.

390
00:40:29,480 --> 00:40:32,160
But why did he do that to me?

391
00:40:41,120 --> 00:40:43,760
He loves you.

392
00:40:45,240 --> 00:40:46,399
But you love me.

393
00:40:46,400 --> 00:40:49,560
That's why he tried to kill me?

394
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:51,480
To him...

395
00:40:53,280 --> 00:40:55,320
He can't see you with someone else.

396
00:40:55,880 --> 00:40:59,400
If he can't have you, no one can.

397
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:02,480
He'd rather watch you die.

398
00:41:04,440 --> 00:41:05,520
Thank you.

399
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:08,840
Thank you for saving me.

400
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:15,200
I love you, Husniya.

401
00:41:22,280 --> 00:41:24,760
I love you, Husniya.

402
00:41:26,880 --> 00:41:27,840
Thank you.

403
00:41:56,160 --> 00:41:59,679
I've asked you many times!
Why is it so hard to tell me?

404
00:41:59,680 --> 00:42:01,679
Radwa, please. Listen!

405
00:42:01,680 --> 00:42:03,559
I'm asking you one more time.

406
00:42:03,560 --> 00:42:06,200
Is it true that I gave birth?

407
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:09,240
Where's our child?

408
00:42:10,560 --> 00:42:12,680
Where's our child, Farez?

409
00:42:13,280 --> 00:42:14,879
Answer me!

410
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:16,240
She's dead, darling!

411
00:42:17,520 --> 00:42:19,000
Our child is dead.

412
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:22,680
Thariq killed our baby.

413
00:42:40,640 --> 00:42:47,200
I will kill Thariq Ridzuwan.

414
00:42:53,680 --> 00:42:55,400
Farez!

415
00:42:56,520 --> 00:42:59,000
- Farez. Help me.
- Hey.

416
00:42:59,760 --> 00:43:04,800
Listen. Hey.

417
00:43:07,880 --> 00:43:08,800
I...

418
00:43:09,880 --> 00:43:11,720
I am your husband,

419
00:43:13,320 --> 00:43:14,400
Thariq Ridzuwan.

420
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:18,040
This is our daughter.

421
00:43:19,480 --> 00:43:21,640
Tia Radia binti Thariq Ridzuwan.

422
00:43:23,600 --> 00:43:24,879
You...

423
00:43:24,880 --> 00:43:26,080
You gave her the name.

424
00:43:31,360 --> 00:43:32,280
Darling. Hey...

425
00:43:34,360 --> 00:43:35,360
Every...

426
00:43:35,880 --> 00:43:41,240
The pain we make peace with today...

427
00:43:42,960 --> 00:43:45,400
will be replaced
by something more beautiful.

428
00:43:52,920 --> 00:43:56,880
Leave everything to God.

429
00:43:59,560 --> 00:44:03,040
Let the divine take care of the rest.

430
00:44:10,280 --> 00:44:11,639
Darling...

431
00:44:11,640 --> 00:44:13,240
Do you remember me now?

432
00:45:54,080 --> 00:45:58,280
{\an8}TO BE CONTINUED

433
00:46:08,120 --> 00:46:11,920
{\an8}<i>Our destiny is shaped
by the choices we make.</i>

434
00:46:12,560 --> 00:46:15,319
{\an8}NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW

435
00:46:15,320 --> 00:46:16,600
{\an8}A.

436
00:46:17,520 --> 00:46:18,360
{\an8}R.

437
00:46:21,680 --> 00:46:22,839
{\an8}- Mom!
- Raudhah!

438
00:46:22,840 --> 00:46:26,199
{\an8}- Mom!
- Please.

439
00:46:26,200 --> 00:46:27,840
{\an8}Help me, Mom!

